name: Dogoboros
description:
The snakes are back! Defend your homeland in this realistic simulation of Dog vs Snake. Awaken your Ouroboros potential. Become the DOGOBOROS!

Hint: the snakes cannot reach Ouroboros on an empty stomach!

Made for Tim Ruswick's JimJam #2 Everything but the audio was created from scratch. Sound effects:  freesound.org Music (by TeknoAXE): How Now Brown Cow
